<h1 class="text-center" style=" padding: 2rem 1rem;background-color: #e9ecef;border-radius: .3rem;opacity:0.8;color:#7f5539;font-weight:bold">Accès interdit</h1>
<div class="container-fluid">
<section class="d-flex justify-content-center flex-column align-items-center">
